<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MPB Branding Demonstration</title>
    <style>
        /* MPB Branding Constants */
        :root {
            --mpb-pink: #FF0081;         /* Supercharged Pink */
            --mpb-midnight: #020035;     /* Deep Midnight Blue */
            --mpb-white: #FFFFFF;
            --mpb-off-white: #F8F8F8;
            --font-main: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            background-color: var(--mpb-white);
            color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            padding: 20px 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            background: var(--mpb-white);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            margin-left: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background-color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            color: var(--mpb-white);
            padding: 100px 5%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-content {
            flex: 1;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(40px, 8vw, 72px);
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* The Focus Ring Graphic */
        .focus-ring-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .focus-ring {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            border: 2px solid var(--mpb-pink);
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .focus-ring::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 40px; height: 2px; background: var(--mpb-pink);
        }

        .focus-ring::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -15px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 40px; height: 2px; background: var(--mpb-pink);
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background-color: var(--mpb-pink);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Grid Section */
        .services {
            padding: 80px 5%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--mpb-off-white);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            background: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--mpb-midnight);
        }

        .card-link {
            color: var(--mpb-pink);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Footer Tagline */
        .tagline {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: var(--mpb-pink);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <a href="#" class="logo">MPB</a>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Buy</a>
            <a href="#">Sell</a>
            <a href="#">Trade</a>
            <a href="#" style="color: var(--mpb-pink)">Log In</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>The right way to buy, sell and trade.</h1>
            <p>Join the circular economy for creative gear. Smarter for you, better for the planet.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-ring-container">
            <div class="focus-ring">
                <div style="position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%, -50%); width:200px; height:200px; border:1px dashed rgba(255,0,129,0.3); border-radius:50%;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Buy used gear</h3>
            <p>Every piece of kit is inspected and approved by our experts. 100% genuine photography.</p>
            <a href="#" class="card-link">Shop now &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Sell your kit</h3>
            <p>Get a free instant quote and free insured pickup. Fast, secure payments direct to you.</p>
            <a href="#" class="card-link">Get a quote &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Trade in</h3>
            <p>Upgrade your setup by trading in your old gear. The simplest way to change your kit.</p>
            <a href="#" class="card-link">Start a trade &rarr;</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="tagline">
        CHOOSE USED. CHOOSE BETTER.
    </div>

</body>
</html>